Yeh so I was using next js and had to add this to my next config file
```

/** @type {import('next').NextConfig} */
module.exports = {
  reactStrictMode: true,
  webpack5: true,
  webpack: (config) => {
    config.resolve.fallback = { fs: false, os: false, path: false, crypto: false };

    return config;
  }
}
```
